00:16:45.947 --> 00:16:47.806
in, in Ka- in...

00:16:45.969 --> 00:16:50.024
INS- INSIDE lager in ⟨sh-⟩ in, in AUSCHWITZ, in, in...?

00:16:49.052 --> 00:16:53.622
⟨oys-⟩ dort hot me-... ir veyst, ir veyst vos ⟨di,⟩ sara AUSCH- AUSCHWITZ⟨,⟩

