00:17:00.325 --> 00:17:05.213
UNK yeder hot geven ⟨in zayn, do-⟩... a moshl eyner hot gearbet di zakhn, der anderer hot ge-...

00:17:04.290 --> 00:17:06.477
vu iz geven di fabrik?

00:17:06.214 --> 00:17:12.795
di fabrik iz geven in K- in EINTRACHTSHÜTTE, in, take dort, in di gegnt, ober der plats UNK...

