ikh hob nisht gearb-...

00:17:28.270 --> 00:17:31.673
⟨zey⟩ zenen geven gefangene, zenen geven,

00:17:29.510 --> 00:17:30.510
⟨s-⟩

00:17:31.543 --> 00:17:34.647
neyn, ikh hob nisht gezen mer-veyniker gefangene. kh'hob gezen

00:17:33.349 --> 00:17:34.743
