zey zenen gehat a bazundere UNK dort opge⟨UNK⟩ a sht- a BUI- a BUILD- a BUILDung oder ⟨do-...⟩

00:17:58.712 --> 00:18:00.874
vu me hot undz nisht tsugelozt tsu geyn,

00:18:00.568 --> 00:18:01.844
