00:18:04.973 --> 00:18:06.049
⟨dos iz⟩ gevezn.

00:18:06.049 --> 00:18:09.467
ikh hob gearbet, ven, vi azoy ikh hob ongehoybn tsu arbetn,

00:18:09.467 --> 00:18:14.585
vos, m'hot dokh nisht gekent UNK hot a frantsoyz gearbet oyf di mashin, a shtoys-mashin.

00:18:15.351 --> 00:18:16.681
sh- a sh⟨toys-...⟩

