 v- damols iz geven gut esn,

00:19:04.947 --> 00:19:10.704
ven, ven ikh, ven er hot ge- ve- bay di kanonen arbetn.

00:19:10.954 --> 00:19:16.106
UNK avade, di vos zey hobn gekert di zamd un di gr- GARBAGE mit dem,

00:19:16.106 --> 00:19:21.320
dos, di hobn, hot men nisht gekukt vos er arbet nisht, er arbet nisht, arbet yo,

00:19:21.320 --> 00:19:27.556
ober ⟨a⟩do, di f-, m'hot gebroykht hobn kanonen un m'hot gebroykht hobn farshidene

00:19:27.556 --> 00:19:31.451
PLANES, ⟨PLANS⟩, UNK fa- farshidene zakhn,

